---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Alfonso de la Rocha - Co-founder & CTO at Finisterra Labs. Building distributed systems, blockchain technology, and organizing the world's structured data."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="page">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <header class="page__header animate-fade-in">
        <h1 class="page__title">About</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="about-content">
        <section class="about-section">
          <p class="about-intro">
            Hi, I'm <strong>Alfonso de la Rocha</strong> (also known as <a href="https://twitter.com/adlrocha" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@adlrocha</a> online).
            I'm currently the Co-founder & CTO at <a href="https://finisterra.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Finisterra Labs</a>,
            where we're building infrastructure to organize the world's structured data.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
          <h2>What I'm Building</h2>
          <p>
            At Finisterra Labs, we're working on <strong>Baselight</strong> - a universal database for structured data.
            Think of it as "Google for structured data" - making data accessible, searchable, and useful for everyone.
            We're a small team of ex-Protocol Labs engineers who share a vision of how data should be organized and accessed.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
          <h2>Background</h2>
          <p>
            Before founding Finisterra, I spent <strong>4+ years at Protocol Labs</strong> working on some of the most
            challenging problems in distributed systems and blockchain technology. Some highlights:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>InterPlanetary Consensus (IPC)</strong> - A framework to scale blockchain networks with custom VMs and syscalls</li>
            <li><strong>Filecoin Indexing System</strong> - Core database infrastructure for content routing</li>
            <li><strong>Go-f3</strong> - Fast Finality protocol implementation for Filecoin</li>
            <li><strong>Beyond Bitswap & ResNetLab</strong> - Research on file-exchange and distributed systems</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
          <h2>Interests</h2>
          <p>
            I'm deeply interested in the intersection of distributed systems, blockchain technology, and AI.
            I believe in open-source, decentralization, and building technology that empowers individuals rather than
            concentrating power in the hands of a few.
          </p>
          <p>
            When I'm not coding, I enjoy reading about consensus mechanisms, exploring new programming languages,
            and thinking about how technology can create a more equitable future.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
          <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
          <p>
            I'm always happy to chat about distributed systems, blockchain, AI, or potential collaborations.
          </p>
          <div class="contact-links">
            <a href="https://twitter.com/adlrocha" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/>
              </svg>
              Twitter/X
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/adlrocha" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
